1
00:00:11,930 --> 00:00:13,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's up?</font>

2
00:00:13,860 --> 00:00:16,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thought I heard a bell.</font>

3
00:01:53,000 --> 00:01:58,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#282727">Episode 12</font></font></font>

4
00:01:53,000 --> 00:01:58,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#282727">"A Country Without Lizel"</font></font></font>

5
00:02:00,480 --> 00:02:02,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Could you appraise these, please?</font>

6
00:02:02,990 --> 00:02:04,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Magic stones, huh?</font>

7
00:02:07,040 --> 00:02:08,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? What is this?</font>

8
00:02:10,100 --> 00:02:12,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's something crazy in here.</font>

9
00:02:13,190 --> 00:02:16,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is it fire? No, flame...</font>

10
00:02:16,390 --> 00:02:18,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is this from a boss?</font>

11
00:02:18,810 --> 00:02:21,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Indeed. That apparently came from 
the boss of the Spirit Garden.</font>

12
00:02:21,970 --> 00:02:25,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They found quite a lot,
so after setting some aside,</font>

13
00:02:25,650 --> 00:02:29,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">he said he'd "offer the 
rest to the market."</font>

14
00:02:29,900 --> 00:02:31,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mr. Lizel...</font>

15
00:02:31,760 --> 00:02:33,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Was he hurt?</font>

16
00:02:33,540 --> 00:02:38,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If the two powerful men with him 
somehow allowed him to become injured,</font>

17
00:02:38,980 --> 00:02:41,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">they wouldn't deserve to live.</font>

18
00:02:41,370 --> 00:02:43,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good, so he's not hurt.</font>

19
00:02:44,450 --> 00:02:48,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This one's worth three gold, 
and this one's five silver.</font>

20
00:02:49,770 --> 00:02:53,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You recognize Eleven's skill, too?</font>

21
00:02:53,290 --> 00:02:55,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm kind of surprised.</font>

22
00:02:55,700 --> 00:02:59,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How could I not, when he 
welcomed him into his party?</font>

23
00:03:00,400 --> 00:03:01,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Also...</font>

24
00:03:01,520 --> 00:03:05,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I believe I said "if," dullard.</font>

25
00:03:05,750 --> 00:03:07,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why are you insulting me?</font>

26
00:03:08,200 --> 00:03:09,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's next?</font>

27
00:03:10,580 --> 00:03:14,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This one's two silver, 
that one's three silver.</font>

28
00:03:17,650 --> 00:03:22,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Those back-to-back award 
ceremonies were unbearable.</font>

29
00:03:22,620 --> 00:03:26,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't say that. It's your duty as a noble.</font>

30
00:03:29,010 --> 00:03:31,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I heard mention of a promotion to count.</font>

31
00:03:31,810 --> 00:03:36,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Apparently, but the idea was abandoned 
out of consideration for the knights.</font>

32
00:03:36,780 --> 00:03:39,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That said, I'd intended to turn it down.</font>

33
00:03:39,860 --> 00:03:43,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The police who accept all backgrounds</font>

34
00:03:43,840 --> 00:03:47,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and knights who value strength 
and lineage don't get along.</font>

35
00:03:48,840 --> 00:03:51,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's hardly a terrible relationship,</font>

36
00:03:51,200 --> 00:03:55,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but nothing can be done about 
differences in principles.</font>

37
00:03:55,500 --> 00:04:00,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A certain marquis demanded to know 
why I didn't immediately report</font>

38
00:04:00,080 --> 00:04:03,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">that I'd found the bandit bases.</font>

39
00:04:03,340 --> 00:04:06,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The one who controls the knights?</font>

40
00:04:07,850 --> 00:04:11,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. He's not wrong, though.</font>

41
00:04:14,230 --> 00:04:17,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>My source was shady.</i></font>

42
00:04:17,610 --> 00:04:21,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I couldn't put that on the knights 
when they're this nation's light.</i></font>

43
00:04:22,740 --> 00:04:24,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now then.</font>

44
00:04:24,360 --> 00:04:28,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Has the boss of the Forky Gang confessed?</font>

45
00:04:28,740 --> 00:04:31,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. Finally, just a moment ago.</font>

46
00:04:31,940 --> 00:04:34,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see. He was tenacious.</font>

47
00:04:36,130 --> 00:04:39,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now everything has been 
wrapped up nicely.</font>

48
00:04:39,440 --> 00:04:41,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good work, sir.</font>

49
00:04:42,690 --> 00:04:46,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And he directed it impressively.</i></font>

50
00:04:48,360 --> 00:04:54,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Anyway, I wish people would stop 
recommending marriage to me</font>

51
00:04:54,050 --> 00:04:56,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">as soon as they see my face.</font>

52
00:04:56,450 --> 00:05:02,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sure many ladies would 
gladly be your second wife.</font>

53
00:05:02,310 --> 00:05:06,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I keep telling them I already have 
an heir, but they won't stop.</font>

54
00:05:06,730 --> 00:05:12,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But you aren't determined 
not to remarry, are you?</font>

55
00:05:12,720 --> 00:05:14,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I suppose not.</font>

56
00:05:14,830 --> 00:05:19,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If I somehow met a greater 
woman, I might consider it.</font>

57
00:05:19,800 --> 00:05:24,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your wife was strong, 
beautiful, and wise.</font>

58
00:05:24,700 --> 00:05:29,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Women greater than her are rare.</font>

59
00:05:29,850 --> 00:05:31,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Indeed.</font>

60
00:05:31,720 --> 00:05:35,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It seems my life will end 
with me serving you.</font>

61
00:05:35,990 --> 00:05:40,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, but if Mr. Lizel were a woman,</font>

62
00:05:40,850 --> 00:05:44,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I would've relentlessly 
attempted to seduce him.</font>

63
00:05:44,790 --> 00:05:47,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I believe you're already doing that.</font>

64
00:05:47,900 --> 00:05:50,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Times New Roman"><font size="30"><font color="#f0edeb">Marcade</font></font></font></font>

65
00:05:50,370 --> 00:05:52,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I picked a fight with 
the merchant's guild.</font>

66
00:05:53,290 --> 00:05:59,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Absolutely not. You know
I reject all their meddling.</font>

67
00:05:59,530 --> 00:06:00,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

68
00:06:01,030 --> 00:06:04,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And that I'm careful not 
to antagonize them.</font>

69
00:06:05,380 --> 00:06:08,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But they really screwed my grandson.</font>

70
00:06:08,930 --> 00:06:12,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? You mean that scandal?</font>

71
00:06:12,610 --> 00:06:16,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah. You know who told me?</font>

72
00:06:16,880 --> 00:06:20,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">An adventurer with a face 
that puts nobles to shame.</font>

73
00:06:21,640 --> 00:06:23,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What does it say?</font>

74
00:06:23,710 --> 00:06:26,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You wanna know? Huh?</font>

75
00:06:27,800 --> 00:06:31,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's primarily about Judge's preferences.</font>

76
00:06:31,730 --> 00:06:32,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

77
00:06:32,700 --> 00:06:34,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He wants to cheer him up.</font>

78
00:06:35,740 --> 00:06:37,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's all?</font>

79
00:06:37,380 --> 00:06:39,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course not.</font>

80
00:06:40,110 --> 00:06:44,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It lists every stolen item the staff 
member in question sold in the past</font>

81
00:06:44,550 --> 00:06:48,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and every guild employee who knew 
about it, among other things.</font>

82
00:06:48,880 --> 00:06:53,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's <i>packed</i> with information that 
could bring down the entire guild.</font>

83
00:06:54,810 --> 00:06:58,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What kind of information 
network does that man have?</font>

84
00:06:58,560 --> 00:07:02,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hold on. Have you mentioned 
this to the guild?</font>

85
00:07:02,100 --> 00:07:04,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nah, not outright.</font>

86
00:07:04,640 --> 00:07:05,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

87
00:07:05,590 --> 00:07:07,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I did hint at it.</font>

88
00:07:07,310 --> 00:07:08,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Absolutely not.</font>

89
00:07:08,990 --> 00:07:12,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This could upset the balance 
of power with the guild.</font>

90
00:07:13,060 --> 00:07:14,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How much did you tell them?</font>

91
00:07:14,530 --> 00:07:17,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I just told them off for 
screwing my grandson.</font>

92
00:07:17,550 --> 00:07:21,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And to get rid of those 
embarrassments to the guild.</font>

93
00:07:21,990 --> 00:07:24,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You should've stopped 
after the first part.</font>

94
00:07:24,510 --> 00:07:28,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They tried to hide things from me, too.</font>

95
00:07:28,220 --> 00:07:30,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They think they can screw me over.</font>

96
00:07:31,870 --> 00:07:37,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And if he told me, that means he 
wants me to do something, right?</font>

97
00:07:37,460 --> 00:07:40,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'd let an adventurer 
tell you what to do?</font>

98
00:07:40,870 --> 00:07:43,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Didn't he make you buy dinner for him?</font>

99
00:07:44,570 --> 00:07:46,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you've concluded your 
business, then leave.</font>

100
00:07:49,310 --> 00:07:51,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry to have bothered you.</font>

101
00:07:58,670 --> 00:08:02,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The Forky Gang was brought 
down at the same time.</i></font>

102
00:08:03,470 --> 00:08:04,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>No...</i></font>

103
00:08:06,520 --> 00:08:08,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It couldn't be.</i></font>

104
00:08:10,410 --> 00:08:12,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What was that, a sneeze?</font>

105
00:08:12,650 --> 00:08:14,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you have a cold, leader?</font>

106
00:08:14,300 --> 00:08:17,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No. Perhaps someone's talking about me.</font>

107
00:08:17,820 --> 00:08:20,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If it worked that way, 
you'd never stop sneezing.</i></font>

108
00:08:21,120 --> 00:08:22,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What should we do today?</font>

109
00:08:22,880 --> 00:08:24,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whatever you want.</font>

110
00:08:28,330 --> 00:08:32,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Think you're strong? Help wanted 
producing healing potions."</font>

111
00:08:32,510 --> 00:08:34,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'd like this, leader.</font>

112
00:08:34,360 --> 00:08:38,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've been wanting to see how 
healing potions are made here.</font>

113
00:08:39,200 --> 00:08:41,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Am I that strong, though?</font>

114
00:08:41,680 --> 00:08:42,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No.</font>

115
00:08:43,840 --> 00:08:46,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just have the Blade do it.</font>

116
00:08:46,250 --> 00:08:50,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not sure about having the great 
Blade take on an F-rank job.</font>

117
00:08:50,930 --> 00:08:52,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We did one before.</font>

118
00:08:56,830 --> 00:08:59,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You were just looking after me then.</font>

119
00:08:59,450 --> 00:09:01,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're the leader.</font>

120
00:09:01,130 --> 00:09:02,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll go with you.</font>

121
00:09:02,900 --> 00:09:07,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But only one of us is strong.</font>

122
00:09:10,400 --> 00:09:13,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't seem much stronger than me.</font>

123
00:09:13,680 --> 00:09:15,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You underestimate me.</font>

124
00:09:15,220 --> 00:09:16,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And you underestimate me.</font>

125
00:09:16,540 --> 00:09:20,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I may not be as strong as 
him, but I do wield blades.</font>

126
00:09:20,930 --> 00:09:23,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then let's arm wrestle.</font>

127
00:09:23,500 --> 00:09:27,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Seriously? You think you can beat me?</font>

128
00:09:27,820 --> 00:09:30,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think I can put up a good fight.</font>

129
00:09:32,220 --> 00:09:33,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Begin.</font>

130
00:09:40,200 --> 00:09:41,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I win.</font>

131
00:09:43,290 --> 00:09:45,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm a bit shocked.</font>

132
00:09:46,420 --> 00:09:50,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thought you fought 
primarily with technique.</font>

133
00:09:50,640 --> 00:09:52,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're not wrong.</font>

134
00:09:52,630 --> 00:09:56,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No matter how skilled you are,
you need strength to cut a golem.</font>

135
00:09:56,850 --> 00:10:00,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then the two of you 
will complete the job.</font>

136
00:10:00,780 --> 00:10:03,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thought you didn't 
want to make him do it.</font>

137
00:10:03,680 --> 00:10:05,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is just how he is.</font>

138
00:10:06,940 --> 00:10:08,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm off to make a delivery.</font>

139
00:10:09,260 --> 00:10:11,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Make sure you stop by the police station.</font>

140
00:10:11,300 --> 00:10:13,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, I know.</font>

141
00:10:17,300 --> 00:10:20,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hello. We're here for the job.</font>

142
00:10:28,660 --> 00:10:30,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm Medi. I'm an apothecary.</font>

143
00:10:30,980 --> 00:10:33,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I like quiet and intelligent people.</font>

144
00:10:33,810 --> 00:10:35,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even better if they're handsome.</font>

145
00:10:35,810 --> 00:10:37,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're exactly my type.</font>

146
00:10:37,270 --> 00:10:40,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Marry me now so we can 
get married someday!</font>

147
00:10:40,490 --> 00:10:41,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're leaving.</font>

148
00:10:41,440 --> 00:10:43,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't make eye contact.</font>

149
00:10:43,170 --> 00:10:45,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll make you happy! I promise!</font>

150
00:10:46,240 --> 00:10:48,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you doing, girl?</font>

151
00:10:51,440 --> 00:10:54,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're not looking for S-rank adventurers.</font>

152
00:10:54,090 --> 00:10:56,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Actually, I'm E-rank. Is that a problem?</font>

153
00:10:57,730 --> 00:10:59,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've got a mouth on you.</font>

154
00:10:59,770 --> 00:11:03,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not paying more than I said I would.</font>

155
00:11:04,240 --> 00:11:08,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry for losing my composure 
because you're exactly my type.</font>

156
00:11:08,590 --> 00:11:11,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's all right. Don't worry about it.</font>

157
00:11:12,320 --> 00:11:14,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So polite!</font>

158
00:11:18,040 --> 00:11:21,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We want you to grind magic stones.</font>

159
00:11:22,100 --> 00:11:23,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'll use this.</font>

160
00:11:23,900 --> 00:11:26,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You put the stones in here.</font>

161
00:11:26,410 --> 00:11:29,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Turn this, and powder will 
come out the bottom.</font>

162
00:11:29,780 --> 00:11:31,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh.</font>

163
00:11:32,770 --> 00:11:35,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It won't budge.</font>

164
00:11:35,600 --> 00:11:37,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course not.</font>

165
00:11:37,540 --> 00:11:41,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Three grown men can barely 
turn it together.</font>

166
00:11:42,160 --> 00:11:45,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you can't do it, 
you can call in help to...</font>

167
00:11:45,940 --> 00:11:47,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Look at it go.</font>

168
00:11:49,080 --> 00:11:50,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How is it, Gil?</font>

169
00:11:50,910 --> 00:11:52,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fine.</font>

170
00:11:53,050 --> 00:11:55,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I guess you won't need any.</font>

171
00:11:55,140 --> 00:11:58,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Impressive. No wonder people 
think you can't be human.</font>

172
00:11:58,670 --> 00:12:00,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're the only one who thinks that.</font>

173
00:12:00,040 --> 00:12:01,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, actually...</font>

174
00:12:01,470 --> 00:12:02,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey.</font>

175
00:12:02,430 --> 00:12:06,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You could probably crush 
them with your bare hands.</font>

176
00:12:06,130 --> 00:12:08,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They probably can't be used to</font>

177
00:12:08,520 --> 00:12:10,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">make healing potions unless
they're a fine powder.</font>

178
00:12:10,760 --> 00:12:13,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop assuming I can do that.</font>

179
00:12:14,270 --> 00:12:16,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This is an insane conversation.</i></font>

180
00:12:17,160 --> 00:12:19,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Keep pouring in the stones.</font>

181
00:12:19,950 --> 00:12:21,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We need all of these crushed.</font>

182
00:12:21,710 --> 00:12:22,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure.</font>

183
00:12:22,760 --> 00:12:26,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Since Gil can do it by himself, 
we're hardly needed.</font>

184
00:12:27,080 --> 00:12:30,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's plenty more to do here.</font>

185
00:12:30,100 --> 00:12:33,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you don't mind, we'll assist you.</font>

186
00:12:33,260 --> 00:12:36,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really? How are you at math?</font>

187
00:12:36,720 --> 00:12:38,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not terrible.</font>

188
00:12:38,320 --> 00:12:41,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I am.</font>

189
00:12:41,910 --> 00:12:43,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is it.</font>

190
00:12:45,920 --> 00:12:48,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ugh, that goes right over my head.</font>

191
00:12:48,640 --> 00:12:50,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can you solve this?</font>

192
00:12:50,640 --> 00:12:54,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't know what I'm doing, but barely.</font>

193
00:12:54,000 --> 00:12:55,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course.</font>

194
00:12:56,240 --> 00:12:58,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I should be able to do this.</font>

195
00:12:58,630 --> 00:13:00,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is this what you want me to do?</font>

196
00:13:01,870 --> 00:13:04,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's as smart as he looks!</font>

197
00:13:05,550 --> 00:13:07,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">May I borrow a desk?</font>

198
00:13:08,420 --> 00:13:10,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, of course!</font>

199
00:13:12,060 --> 00:13:14,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'd look great writing with a pen!</font>

200
00:13:14,570 --> 00:13:16,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Marry me!</font>

201
00:13:16,880 --> 00:13:17,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you wear glasses?</font>

202
00:13:17,970 --> 00:13:19,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My vision is good.</font>

203
00:13:22,940 --> 00:13:25,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't do this.</font>

204
00:13:25,460 --> 00:13:28,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then why don't you help with deliveries?</font>

205
00:13:28,540 --> 00:13:31,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If the apothecary doesn't mind, that is.</font>

206
00:13:31,770 --> 00:13:33,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That would be a huge help.</font>

207
00:13:33,380 --> 00:13:35,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm glad to hear that.</font>

208
00:13:35,040 --> 00:13:39,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't worry. He can handle most things.</font>

209
00:13:39,300 --> 00:13:40,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know about that?</font>

210
00:13:40,490 --> 00:13:44,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, but I heard you mention the police 
earlier, so I thought maybe...</font>

211
00:13:45,020 --> 00:13:50,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lately, I've been hearing a lot about 
potion deliveries being stolen.</font>

212
00:13:50,940 --> 00:13:52,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We were attacked once,</font>

213
00:13:52,980 --> 00:13:56,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but the old fart was making the 
delivery, so it worked out.</font>

214
00:13:57,750 --> 00:13:59,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, he'd be just fine.</font>

215
00:14:00,210 --> 00:14:04,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We can't mass produce these, 
so any thefts are a huge loss.</font>

216
00:14:04,440 --> 00:14:06,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who's even stealing our product?</font>

217
00:14:07,920 --> 00:14:09,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not me.</font>

218
00:14:09,670 --> 00:14:11,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's not what I meant.</font>

219
00:14:11,120 --> 00:14:14,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can fend thieves off 
if you're attacked, right?</font>

220
00:14:14,070 --> 00:14:16,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course. Can I kill them?</font>

221
00:14:16,680 --> 00:14:17,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No.</font>

222
00:14:17,850 --> 00:14:19,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Got it.</font>

223
00:14:20,730 --> 00:14:23,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I'm off.</font>

224
00:14:23,980 --> 00:14:26,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is he okay?</font>

225
00:14:26,040 --> 00:14:28,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's fine. He's quite skilled.</font>

226
00:14:28,970 --> 00:14:32,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Anyway, should we leave 
the ground stones there?</font>

227
00:14:33,580 --> 00:14:36,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's a ton of powder. That was quick.</font>

228
00:14:38,000 --> 00:14:41,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mr. Brains, give me the calculations 
as soon as you complete them.</font>

229
00:14:41,380 --> 00:14:43,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I need them for the magic stones.</font>

230
00:14:43,410 --> 00:14:44,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Understood.</font>

231
00:14:47,110 --> 00:14:49,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm back.</font>

232
00:14:49,660 --> 00:14:52,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Welcome back. You weren't gone long.</font>

233
00:14:53,320 --> 00:14:56,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Glasses?! Are they fake?</font>

234
00:14:56,640 --> 00:14:58,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why are you wearing those?</font>

235
00:14:58,410 --> 00:15:02,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was told wearing them would be 
motivating and increase efficiency.</font>

236
00:15:05,230 --> 00:15:07,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I just can't get used to them.</font>

237
00:15:07,350 --> 00:15:09,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take them off if they're bothering you.</font>

238
00:15:09,600 --> 00:15:11,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was going to...</font>

239
00:15:12,180 --> 00:15:14,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but strangely, they seem to be working.</font>

240
00:15:16,840 --> 00:15:18,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, quit staring.</font>

241
00:15:19,130 --> 00:15:21,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Looks like you successfully 
completed the delivery.</font>

242
00:15:21,840 --> 00:15:23,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here's the money.</font>

243
00:15:23,130 --> 00:15:25,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And you weren't attacked 
by thieves either.</font>

244
00:15:25,740 --> 00:15:28,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Actually, I was.</font>

245
00:15:28,100 --> 00:15:29,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

246
00:15:29,490 --> 00:15:30,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How did it go?</font>

247
00:15:30,990 --> 00:15:32,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I fought them off, no problem.</font>

248
00:15:32,860 --> 00:15:36,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They weren't bandits, just arrogant 
brats looking to fill their pockets.</font>

249
00:15:36,570 --> 00:15:40,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Perhaps a merchant hoping to 
resell put them up to it.</font>

250
00:15:41,160 --> 00:15:42,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What did you do with the children?</font>

251
00:15:42,790 --> 00:15:44,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I ditched 'em.</font>

252
00:15:44,040 --> 00:15:45,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

253
00:15:45,050 --> 00:15:50,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, but I ran into a cop I've seen 
before, so I let him handle it.</font>

254
00:15:50,340 --> 00:15:53,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is there anything else to do? I'm bored.</font>

255
00:15:54,000 --> 00:15:54,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, you.</font>

256
00:15:55,530 --> 00:16:01,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mr. Brains is solving those complex 
problems like it's nothing.</font>

257
00:16:01,180 --> 00:16:02,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's his deal?</font>

258
00:16:02,540 --> 00:16:05,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Our great leader is amazing.</font>

259
00:16:06,380 --> 00:16:09,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's fetching in glasses, 
has beautiful skin,</font>

260
00:16:09,310 --> 00:16:12,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and he's stoic, but he's sexy, too? 
He's a walking contradiction.</font>

261
00:16:12,980 --> 00:16:14,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But that's what I like.</font>

262
00:16:14,520 --> 00:16:15,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You sound like an old guy.</font>

263
00:16:16,370 --> 00:16:18,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's his type?</font>

264
00:16:19,090 --> 00:16:22,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't know. Girly girls, probably.</font>

265
00:16:22,620 --> 00:16:24,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Like me?</font>

266
00:16:24,040 --> 00:16:25,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What did I just say?</font>

267
00:16:26,280 --> 00:16:28,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What's his type, huh?</i></font>

268
00:16:30,000 --> 00:16:33,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The things I'd do to that chaste face...</font>

269
00:16:34,300 --> 00:16:38,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Could you not talk about him like that?</font>

270
00:16:38,540 --> 00:16:40,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Maybe I could...</font>

271
00:16:41,210 --> 00:16:44,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I told you to stop! I'll kill you, bitch!</font>

272
00:16:44,880 --> 00:16:46,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Language, Eleven.</font>

273
00:16:46,950 --> 00:16:48,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No fair!</font>

274
00:16:51,240 --> 00:16:53,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm tired.</font>

275
00:16:54,020 --> 00:16:56,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You just rested after 
completing the delivery.</font>

276
00:16:56,870 --> 00:16:59,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gil was grinding the whole time.</font>

277
00:16:59,030 --> 00:17:01,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My arms are pretty tired.</font>

278
00:17:01,110 --> 00:17:03,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I mean I'm mentally exhausted.</font>

279
00:17:04,050 --> 00:17:08,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's wrong with that 
man-eater—no, man-needer?</font>

280
00:17:08,820 --> 00:17:11,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, that was pretty clever.</font>

281
00:17:15,070 --> 00:17:16,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's wrong?</font>

282
00:17:16,480 --> 00:17:18,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thought I heard a bell.</font>

283
00:17:20,900 --> 00:17:23,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I must've imagined it.</i></font>

284
00:17:28,700 --> 00:17:31,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">By the way, what's your type?</font>

285
00:17:31,760 --> 00:17:33,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My type?</font>

286
00:17:33,150 --> 00:17:36,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As in who tends to catch your eye.</font>

287
00:17:36,080 --> 00:17:41,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wouldn't call them my type,
but they're exactly around your age.</font>

288
00:17:41,660 --> 00:17:43,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know someone my age?</font>

289
00:17:44,230 --> 00:17:47,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, the most important 
person in the world to me.</font>

290
00:17:47,390 --> 00:17:49,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? Who? A woman? Is it?</font>

291
00:17:50,420 --> 00:17:52,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who's to say?</font>

292
00:17:53,490 --> 00:17:57,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There it is again. 
A bell failing to ring properly.</font>

293
00:17:57,830 --> 00:17:58,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you hear that?</font>

294
00:17:58,940 --> 00:18:00,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No.</font>

295
00:18:00,360 --> 00:18:01,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Same.</font>

296
00:18:02,600 --> 00:18:05,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Am I hearing things? No...</i></font>

297
00:18:05,450 --> 00:18:06,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you okay?</font>

298
00:18:06,980 --> 00:18:08,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you sleep last night?</font>

299
00:18:08,620 --> 00:18:10,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, soundly.</font>

300
00:18:15,210 --> 00:18:16,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not these.</font>

301
00:18:19,230 --> 00:18:21,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry.</font>

302
00:18:22,130 --> 00:18:23,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not mad.</font>

303
00:18:25,760 --> 00:18:30,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If only you can hear it, it could 
have something to do with those.</font>

304
00:18:31,920 --> 00:18:34,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are those related to 
your important person?</font>

305
00:18:35,050 --> 00:18:36,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's a secret.</font>

306
00:18:44,180 --> 00:18:46,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's going on?</font>

307
00:18:47,030 --> 00:18:48,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Leader!</font>

308
00:18:48,610 --> 00:18:50,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's breathing. Is he poisoned?</font>

309
00:18:51,030 --> 00:18:52,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't smell anything.</font>

310
00:18:54,030 --> 00:18:54,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lea—</font>

311
00:18:55,820 --> 00:18:57,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How long was I out?</font>

312
00:18:58,180 --> 00:18:59,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A little over ten seconds.</font>

313
00:18:59,620 --> 00:19:01,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, that long?</font>

314
00:19:01,590 --> 00:19:02,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you okay?</font>

315
00:19:02,880 --> 00:19:04,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I feel great.</font>

316
00:19:05,350 --> 00:19:08,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I feel as though a ton of 
mana was poured into me.</font>

317
00:19:08,990 --> 00:19:10,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is this...?</font>

318
00:19:18,260 --> 00:19:19,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This mana...</i></font>

319
00:19:22,760 --> 00:19:24,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'd never forget it.</i></font>

320
00:19:41,270 --> 00:19:42,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Majesty.</font>

321
00:19:43,490 --> 00:19:46,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, did you get through to him already?</font>

322
00:19:46,110 --> 00:19:49,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, who do you think you're 
standing in front of?</font>

323
00:19:49,400 --> 00:19:50,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is this?</font>

324
00:19:50,570 --> 00:19:52,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How should I know?</font>

325
00:19:52,750 --> 00:19:56,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Majesty, Father, 
I'm glad you both seem well.</font>

326
00:19:56,840 --> 00:20:00,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So do you. Oh, I'm so glad.</font>

327
00:20:00,220 --> 00:20:03,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you weren't his father, 
I'd have you put to death.</font>

328
00:20:03,300 --> 00:20:04,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you even listening?</font>

329
00:20:04,420 --> 00:20:05,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Step aside, damn it!</font>

330
00:20:05,690 --> 00:20:09,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you have any idea what it 
took to open this window?</font>

331
00:20:09,080 --> 00:20:10,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He's just like him.</i></font>

332
00:20:10,400 --> 00:20:14,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">May I assume I'm in another world?</font>

333
00:20:14,710 --> 00:20:15,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

334
00:20:15,770 --> 00:20:21,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Unfortunately, it'll be a while 
longer before we can come get you.</font>

335
00:20:21,360 --> 00:20:23,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then I'll wait patiently.</font>

336
00:20:23,470 --> 00:20:25,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you doing now?</font>

337
00:20:25,940 --> 00:20:28,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm enjoying being an adventurer.</font>

338
00:20:28,480 --> 00:20:31,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">An adventurer? That sounds fun.</font>

339
00:20:31,400 --> 00:20:33,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just try not to get hurt.</font>

340
00:20:33,700 --> 00:20:36,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He has his father's approval?</i></font>

341
00:20:36,480 --> 00:20:38,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are those two behind you your friends?</font>

342
00:20:38,770 --> 00:20:41,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. We adventure together.</font>

343
00:20:44,320 --> 00:20:47,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't look very nice, 
but you seem like a knight.</font>

344
00:20:47,490 --> 00:20:50,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sure you'll do a good 
job protecting Lizel.</font>

345
00:20:51,030 --> 00:20:54,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And you look like the 
boss of a bandit gang.</font>

346
00:20:54,540 --> 00:20:56,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, that's not an insult.</font>

347
00:20:57,400 --> 00:20:58,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks.</font>

348
00:20:59,330 --> 00:21:02,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm relieved you both seem dependable.</font>

349
00:21:02,210 --> 00:21:05,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I told you to <i>move</i>! 
Do I need to command you?</font>

350
00:21:07,220 --> 00:21:09,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Have fun, Lizel.</font>

351
00:21:10,750 --> 00:21:11,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Liz.</font>

352
00:21:12,970 --> 00:21:15,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A country without you is worthless.</font>

353
00:21:19,890 --> 00:21:21,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait for me.</font>

354
00:21:24,800 --> 00:21:27,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I promise I'll bring you back.</font>

355
00:21:34,450 --> 00:21:35,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, sir.</font>

356
00:21:46,190 --> 00:21:47,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Next.</font>

357
00:21:54,940 --> 00:21:56,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A noble?</font>

358
00:21:56,700 --> 00:21:58,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're confusing people again.</font>

359
00:21:58,590 --> 00:22:00,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This always happens.</font>

360
00:22:00,300 --> 00:22:02,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not my fault.</font>

361
00:22:02,550 --> 00:22:04,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uh, what is your reason for entry?</font>

362
